<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.8.4">
<l>ōṭā variyā yiraṇiyaṉai yūṉiṭanta</l>
<l>cēṭār poḻilcūḻ tirunīr malaiyāṉai</l>
<l>vāṭā malarttuḻāy mālai muṭiyāṉai</l>
<l>nāṭōṟum nāṭi naṟaiyūril kaṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having searched daily for the one of Tirunīrmalai,</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by beautiful groves,</l>
<l>Who, as a never-fleeing lion, gouged the flesh of Hiraṇya,</l>
<l>The one on whose crown is a garland of never-withering tulasī blossoms,</l>
<l>I saw [him] in Naṟaiyūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
